text: Ðis syndon ðara V hida landgemæro æt Wigli ðe æðelwold and ælfhelm his broðor hæddan.
Ærest of Hunighamme westewearden up andlang streames on ða ealdan dic.
Of ðære ealdan dic swa on bican dune westewearde.
Of bican dune on ðene hricweg.
Ðonne east andlang hricweges on ða ealdan furh.
Of ðære ealdan furh andlangan dune.
Forewearde of langan dune on loc hylle.
Ðis is ðære V hida land boc to Wilig ðæ æðelred cing gebocade ælfgar bisceope on æce yrfe.
